  "detailed_description": "A summoning has gone wrong. Now the house and all plushies are possessed.<br>Can you make it through the maze, activate all symbols and defeat the demon?<br><br>Plush Madness is a Horror Fighting Game optimized for VR and playable for Flatscreen too.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat Plushies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/3bcf19f15aff908ab1197e5fce56143b.poster.avif?t=1727862000\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/3bcf19f15aff908ab1197e5fce56143b.webm?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/3bcf19f15aff908ab1197e5fce56143b.mp4?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In every room, you'll see plushies trying to attack you.<br>You can pick them up, rip them apart or just hit them and make them fly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Activate Symbols</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/625a87d11d1a500ca8688add3c48382d.poster.avif?t=1727862000\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/625a87d11d1a500ca8688add3c48382d.webm?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/625a87d11d1a500ca8688add3c48382d.mp4?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll have to activate the symbols in the correct order to open the last door in the basement.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Limit</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/8469ad125574deaea30479b7757a3c94.poster.avif?t=1727862000\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/8469ad125574deaea30479b7757a3c94.webm?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/8469ad125574deaea30479b7757a3c94.mp4?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is a Time Limit on your hands. Whenever you defeat a plushie, the timer is incremented.<br>Can you make it to the end without running out of time?",
  "about_the_game": "A summoning has gone wrong. Now the house and all plushies are possessed.<br>Can you make it through the maze, activate all symbols and defeat the demon?<br><br>Plush Madness is a Horror Fighting Game optimized for VR and playable for Flatscreen too.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat Plushies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/3bcf19f15aff908ab1197e5fce56143b.poster.avif?t=1727862000\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/3bcf19f15aff908ab1197e5fce56143b.webm?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/3bcf19f15aff908ab1197e5fce56143b.mp4?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In every room, you'll see plushies trying to attack you.<br>You can pick them up, rip them apart or just hit them and make them fly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Activate Symbols</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/625a87d11d1a500ca8688add3c48382d.poster.avif?t=1727862000\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/625a87d11d1a500ca8688add3c48382d.webm?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/625a87d11d1a500ca8688add3c48382d.mp4?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll have to activate the symbols in the correct order to open the last door in the basement.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Limit</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/8469ad125574deaea30479b7757a3c94.poster.avif?t=1727862000\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/8469ad125574deaea30479b7757a3c94.webm?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1686570/extras/8469ad125574deaea30479b7757a3c94.mp4?t=1727862000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is a Time Limit on your hands. Whenever you defeat a plushie, the timer is incremented.<br>Can you make it to the end without running out of time?",
